POINTE NOIRE, Congo (Republic of the), February 9, 2018/APO Group/ --
                                                
                        Africanews (www.Africanews.com), a leading multilingual and Pan-African news outlet is now available to all device mobile owners through its apps designed to run on iOS and Android.
        
                
            
                
                                
                
                
